init_lef_check_antenna(25.10)                    init_lef_check_antenna(25.10)

Name
       init_lef_check_antenna

Syntax
       init_lef_check_antenna {0 | 1}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: 1

       If  you  set  init_lef_check_antenna to true, LEF or OA cells will have
       process antenna consistency checks done for LEF ANTENNA*  data  (or  OA
       equivalent  data) attached to their pins.  Input pins with 0 gate-area,
       output pins with 0 diff-area, and inout pins  with  0  gate-area  or  0
       diff-area  values  will  generate warnings. If false, the tool will not
       perform consistency checking.

